properties.name: E4000
properties.description: Signals that a data-related error occurred in external code with which the DevExtreme data works.

properties.name: E4001
properties.description: Occurs when the an unknown aggregating function is specified.

properties.name: E4002
properties.description: Occurs when the unsupported OData version in specified for the ODataStore or ODataContext object.

properties.name: E4003
properties.description: Occurs when an unknown filter operation is used.

properties.name: E4004
properties.description: Occurs when the [thenby()].md '/Documentation/ApiReference/Data_Layer/Query/Methods/#thenBygetter') method is called before the [sortby()].md '/Documentation/ApiReference/Data_Layer/Query/Methods/#sortBygetter') method.

properties.name: E4005
properties.description: Occurs when calling a key-dependent method of a store with an unspecified key property.

properties.name: E4006
properties.description: Occurs when the value that is set to the [data] configuration property of the **ArrayStore** object is not an array.

properties.name: E4007
properties.description: Occurs when an auto-generated key is required for a Data Store with a compound key expression.

properties.name: E4008
properties.description: Occurs when items with duplicated keys are inserted.

properties.name: E4009
properties.description: Occurs in a store when its [byKey(key)].md '/Documentation/ApiReference/Data_Layer/ArrayStore/Methods/#byKeykey') function does not return a value.

properties.name: E4010
properties.description: Occurs when creating the [Query] object by using the **createQuery** method of a CustomStore.

properties.name: E4011
properties.description: Occurs when an unimplemented CustomStore method is called.

properties.name: E4012
properties.description: Occurs when a method implemented for a Custom Store returns an unexpected result.

properties.name: E4013
properties.description: Occurs when the [name] property is not specified for a [LocalStore] instance.

properties.name: E4014
properties.description: Occurs when an unknown key type is detected.

properties.name: E4015
properties.description: Occurs when calling the [objectLink(entityAlias, key)].md '/Documentation/ApiReference/Data_Layer/ODataContext/Methods/#objectLinkentityAlias_key') method and passing an entity alias that is not registered for the given [ODataCOntext] object.

properties.name: E4016
properties.description: Occurs when the [compileSetter(expr)].md '/Documentation/ApiReference/Data_Layer/Utils/#compileSetterexpr') method is called with **this** passed as a parameter.

properties.name: E4017
properties.description: Occurs when calling the [update(key,values)] method to modify a key(s).

properties.name: E4018
properties.description: Occurs when the server returns a non-numeric value after the [totalCount].md '/Documentation/ApiReference/Data_Layer/ODataStore/Methods/#totalCountoptions') method of an ODataStore instance is called.

properties.name: E4019
properties.description: Occurs if a [filter expression] contains different group operators within a single group.

properties.name: E4020
properties.description: Occurs if the [store.type] property of a DataSource instance holds an unknown store type.

properties.name: E4021
properties.description: Occurs if [CustomStore].[load] returns an `undefined` [LoadResultObject].**totalCount**, or if the **CustomStore**.[totalCount] method is not specified.

properties.name: E4022
properties.description: Occurs if [CustomStore].[load] returns an `undefined` [LoadResultObject].**groupCount**.

properties.name: E4023
properties.description: Occurs in the [XmlaStore] if the received data cannot be parsed into XML.

properties.name: E4024
properties.description: Occurs in the [ODataStore] when a string function (*"startswith"*, *"endswith"*, *"contains"*, *"notcontains"*) is used to search or filter a non-string data field.

properties.name: Errors and Warnings
properties.description: This section lists errors and warnings that may occur when using the DevExtreme Data Library.

properties.name: W4000
properties.description: Occurs when data returned from a server has an incorrect structure.

properties.name: W4001
properties.description: Occurs in the [ODataStore] when a single field is assigned both to the [keyType] and [fieldTypes] properties. Remove the field's name from one of the properties.

properties.name: W4002
properties.description: Produced by the [XmlaStore] when an error occurs on loading data for certain cells. For details on the error, refer to the XMLA specification.
